				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Player interacts with the third mural of the Mausoleum puzzle and get the final piece of the story. This mural depicts Ketheric Thorm, along with a Sharran army, standing before the corrupted version of Moonrise Towers. Player response varies, depending on if they've seen Ketheric or not. (note: do NOT refer to Moonrise towers by name in these responses, as awareness is not guaranteed)"
